 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Both my board exams were hectic","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:22 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"But was given no exception","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:22 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Stupid people 🙄","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:22 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Can't expect much from them","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:23 pm","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"🙃"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I had to go back to give my 8th sem in COVID cause University was like if you are in 1st, 2nd or 3rd year they will promote based on the previous results but if you are in final year you die but give exam first","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:24 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"The matter literally went to supreme court","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:24 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Do they know particularly we exist ?","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:25 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"And nothing happened","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:25 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"🥹","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:25 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"They don't care","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:25 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I had to be in quarantine for 10 days after reaching Bangalore","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:25 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Alhamdulilah you are fine","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:26 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Or else who would have listened to me","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:26 pm","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😢"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"🥺","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:27 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I would have from some parallel universe","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:28 pm","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"A hypothetical question..if I had missed your profile when u created  .. would you have texted","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:30 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It’s making me think too hard","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:31 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"But I would have","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:31 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:32 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Just like out of curiosity","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:32 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And if you would have responded differently I would have ghosted you","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:33 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"😭","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:33 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Well I just wanted to know why u left from WhatsApp..that was my intention..I was angry..but anger doesn't last for so many days..so, when I saw you I was  like I should ask first if you even remember","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:35 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I was scared as well","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:35 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"To even respond","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:36 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay 😶","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:36 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"But it was good at the end and that's all that matters 😌","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:37 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yepp","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:37 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Ma'am it's quite late ..I shouldn't keep you up now","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:38 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"We shall sleep","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:38 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yess","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:39 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Allah Hafiz","time":"Dec 06, 2023 12:39 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Take care of yourself","time":"Dec 06,